	<h1 class="title">老家具和老建筑，这里有家像集市一样的旗舰店</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/75281/small/75281.jgp?1425220992" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Julie Wolfson</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-06-29 12:12:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/11226/medium/11226.jpeg?1436641619" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


